FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1780405872
OL,3,CDoug Beattie resigns from UUP as
OL,4,Cmembership 'no longer tenable'
OL,6,FThere had been speculation in recent
OL,7,Fweeks that some within the party did
OL,8,Fnot want to see Mr Beattie selected to
OL,9,Frun as a candidate in the Upper Bann
OL,10,Fconstituency ` where he has had a seat
OL,11,Ffor 10 years ` at the next election in
OL,12,F2027.
OL,14,FIn his resignation letter posted on
OL,15,Fsocial media, the ex-Army captain said
OL,16,Fit had become clear to him that his
OL,17,Fposition within the party "is no
OL,18,Flonger tenable".
OL,26,@yD@[OUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1780405872
OL,3,CDoug Beattie resigns from UUP as
OL,4,Cmembership 'no longer tenable'
OL,6,F"Over the last 12 years, I have made
OL,7,Fmany valued friendships within the
OL,8,Fparty, and I sincerely hope those
OL,9,Ffriendships endure," Mr Beattie wrote.
OL,11,F"However, over the past two years I
OL,12,Fhave witnessed a marked deterioration
OL,13,Fin the relationship between the party
OL,14,Fmanagement board, constituency
OL,15,Fassociations, the Ulster Unionist
OL,16,FCouncillor Association, and the MLA
OL,17,Fgroup at Stormont.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@TO]sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1780405872
OL,3,CDoug Beattie resigns from UUP as
OL,4,Cmembership 'no longer tenable'
OL,6,F"This became particularly apparent and
OL,7,Faccelerated following your election as
OL,8,Fparty leader when MLAs were
OL,9,Fincreasingly marginalised, ignored,
OL,10,Fisolated and discredited.
OL,12,F"Your leadership style became
OL,13,Fdismissive and overly centralised,
OL,14,Fempowering individuals to actively
OL,15,Fundermine elected representatives," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"In the absence of any coherent policy
OL,19,Fdirection from the leadership, a toxic
OL,20,Fatmosphere has been allowed to
OL,21,Fflourish within the party.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@cO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1780405872
OL,3,CDoug Beattie resigns from UUP as
OL,4,Cmembership 'no longer tenable'
OL,6,F"The Ulster Unionist Party once prided
OL,7,Fitself on its social conscience, its
OL,8,Fprogressive and moderate outlook, and
OL,9,Fits respected conservative tradition.
OL,11,F"I no longer believe that is the case
OL,12,Fand I no longer feel at home or
OL,13,Fcomfortable within the party."
OL,15,FHe added: "Even as I raised concerns
OL,16,Fdirectly with you, an insidious
OL,17,Fcampaign of rumour and gossip was
OL,18,Fbeing waged against me regarding
OL,19,Fselections, party relationships,
OL,20,Ffinancial matters, and employment
OL,21,Fissues."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@^O]wD@KOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1780405872
OL,3,CDoug Beattie resigns from UUP as
OL,4,Cmembership 'no longer tenable'
OL,6,FMr Beattie further stated that Mr
OL,7,FBurrows rang him announcing his
OL,8,Fintention to "reopen a disciplinary
OL,9,Fmatter" against him, which the Upper
OL,10,FBann MLA described as "vindictive and
OL,11,Fa deliberate attempt to drive" him
OL,12,Ffrom the party.
OL,14,FHe concluded: "I wish the party well
OL,15,Fin the future and hope it can
OL,16,Frediscover its social conscience and
OL,17,Freturn to the path set by Mike Nesbitt
OL,18,FMLA in 2012.
OL,26,@pD@NOUqD@GO]rD@WOUsD@^O]vD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1780405872
OL,3,CDoug Beattie resigns from UUP as
OL,4,Cmembership 'no longer tenable'
OL,6,F"A path that led me to join a party
OL,7,Ffounded on the principle of country
OL,8,Ffirst and party second."
OL,10,FA UUP spokesperson thanked Mr Beattie
OL,11,F"for his many years of service to his
OL,12,Fcountry and to the party" but said it
OL,13,F"does not accept the characterisation
OL,14,Fof recent events set out in Mr
OL,15,FBeattie's letter".
OL,17,F"The party management board met on
OL,18,FThursday evening to consider serious
OL,19,Fconcerns about Mr Beattie's conduct
OL,20,Fand judgment," they said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@XO]sD@AOUtD@YO]uD@AOUwD@QO]yD@
OL,26,AAOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
