CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1780405872
OL,3,CDoug Beattie resigns from UUP as
OL,4,Cmembership 'no longer tenable'
OL,6,F"The board unanimously agreed a course
OL,7,Fof action, which was due to be
OL,8,Fcommunicated to Mr Beattie by the
OL,9,Fparty leader on Monday.
OL,11,F"Mr Beattie's resignation has
OL,12,Fovertaken that process."
OL,14,FThey added: "The party's focus remains
OL,15,Fon serving the people of Northern
OL,16,FIreland, on delivering for them, and
OL,17,Fon the work ahead."
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
